param=param_880,- This item can be used to store any single coordinate, alongside your Hitpoints, Prayer and Special Attack Energy, and teleport back to it at a later date, restoring those stats to what they were.<br><br>- This item ignores wilderness teleport restrictions.<br><br>- The Crystal of Echoes cannot store coordinates whilst inside an instance.<br><br>- There are various other locations this item won't store coordinates in, including quest areas, certain minigames, etc.
