// 1135
[struct_1135]
param=param_879,Last Stand
param=param_880,You gain the <col=#>Last Stand</col> perk, which works as follows:<br><br>- If damage would reduce you to 0 hp, you are reduced to 1 hp instead.<br><br>- Your combat stats are instantly boosted to 255 but begin draining rapidly back down to their base level + 15.<br><br>- For the next 16 ticks after this ability is activated, you cannot be reduced to 0 HP.<br><br>- When the effect ends, all incoming damage is nullified and the player is healed based on the damage they dealt over the last 16 ticks.<br><br>Once this ability is used, it cannot be used again until you die or 3 minutes have passed.
