// 1722
[struct_1722]
param=param_879,Endless Harvest
param=param_880,- You can endlessly gather from Fishing spots, Trees and Mining rocks even if they deplete after your initial interaction.<br><br>- Resources gathered from <col=#>Fishing</col>, <col=#>Woodcutting</col> and <col=#>Mining</col> are multiplied by 2.<br><br>- XP is granted for all additional resources gathered.
