// 1723
[struct_1723]
param=param_879,Production Master
param=param_880,When doing the following <col=#>Production</col> activities, all items are processed at once:<br><br>- smelting ores, Smithing bars and making Cannonballs.<br><br>- Fletching logs, stringing Bows, making arrow shafts and cutting bolt tips.<br><br>- Making headless arrows, regular arrows, bolts and darts (capped at 10x the regular amount per action).<br><br>- Cleaning herbs and making potions which do not have a stackable secondary ingredient.<br><br>- Cooking food, making pies or pizzas and making Jugs of Wine.<br><br>- Crafting leather, uncut gems, glassblowing, jewellery, pottery, Battlestaves and spinning flax or wool.
param=param_884,"league_5_relics_large,13"
param=param_1853,"league_5_relics_medium,13"
param=param_1854,"league_5_relics_medium_off,13"
param=param_881,"league_5_relics,13"
param=param_883,"league_5_relics_off,13"
param=param_882,"league_5_relics_tli,13"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1855,false

// 1724
[struct_1724]
param=param_879,Skilling Prodigy
param=param_880,- All non-combat skills are permanently boosted by +12.<br><br>- The boost from this Relic does not stack with any other weaker boosts but can be overwritten by a stronger one.<br><br>- When using this Relic, skills that are boosted above +12 will over time drain back to the original +12 boost.<br><br>- When using this Relic, skills that are drained below +12 will over time restore back to the original +12 boost.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,4"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,4"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,5"
param=param_885,0
param=param_1274,struct_3061

// 1725
[struct_1725]
param=param_879,Fairy's Flight
param=param_880,- This item will allow you to <col=#>Teleport</col> to any fairy ring, spirit tree, or tool leprechaun.<br><br>- Unlocking this will autocomplete the Tree Gnome Village quest.<br><br>- This item ignores wilderness teleport restrictions.<br><br>- This item cannot be used to teleport to an area you haven't unlocked.
param=param_884,"league_5_relics_large,3"
param=param_1853,"league_5_relics_medium,3"
param=param_1854,"league_5_relics_medium_off,3"
param=param_881,"league_5_relics,3"
param=param_883,"league_5_relics_off,3"
param=param_882,"league_5_relics_tli,3"
param=param_885,2
param=param_1274,struct_3062
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,league_trailblazer_fairys_flight_teleport

// 1726
[struct_1726]
param=param_879,Eternal Jeweller
param=param_880,- The following items no longer consume charges when you teleport with them: Master Scroll Book, Ring of Dueling, Ring of Returning, Games Necklace, Amulet of Glory, Skills Necklace, Combat Bracelet, Digsite Pendant, Necklace of Passage, Slayer Ring and Ring of Wealth.<br><br>- Upon selecting this Relic you will receive the following items: Ring of Dueling, Ring of Returning, Games Necklace, Skills Necklace, Necklace of Passage and Ring of Wealth.<br><br>- This Relic cannot be used to teleport to an area you haven't unlocked.<br><br>- If lost these items cannot be reclaimed from the Sage in Lumbridge.<br><br>- As this Relic gives you an item it must be unlocked at a Bank.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,8"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,8"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,9"
param=param_885,1
param=param_1274,struct_3063
param=param_1855,true

// 1727
[struct_1727]
param=param_879,Last Recall
param=param_880,- Upon selecting this Relic you will receive a Crystal of Memories which when used will teleport you back to the location from where your most recent teleport occurred.<br><br>- Your teleport will only be stored if the Crystal of Memories is in your Inventory. You will receive a message in your chatbox if it successfully stored your previous destination.<br><br>- The Crystal of Memories will not remember your teleport location if you teleport from an instance.<br><br>- There are various other locations this teleport won't save your teleport location, including quest areas, minigames, etc.<br><br>- You cannot teleport using the Crystal of Memories whilst you have a follower.<br><br>- On death, the Crystal of Memories is destroyed and can be reclaimed from the Sage in Lumbridge.<br><br>- As this Relic gives you an item it must be unlocked at a Bank.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,10"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,10"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,11"
param=param_885,1
param=param_1274,struct_3064
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,league_trailblazer_last_recall_teleport

// 1728
[struct_1728]
param=param_879,Quick Shot
param=param_880,- The attack speed of all Ranged weapons is halved (rounded up).<br><br>- Your ranged attacks have 100% increased accuracy against creatures and 50% increased accuracy against other players.<br><br>- Your Ranged attacks deal 10% more damage.<br><br>- You save 90% of your ammunition when firing Ranged weapons. This does not include chinchompas but does include Crystal Bow, Toxic Blowpipe and Craw's Bow charges.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,12"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,12"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,13"
param=param_885,2
param=param_1274,struct_3065

// 1729
[struct_1729]
param=param_879,Fluid Strikes
param=param_880,- The attack speed of all melee weapons is halved (rounded up).<br><br>- Your melee attacks have 25% increased accuracy.<br><br>- You take 15% less damage from all sources.<br><br>- Your Hitpoints regenerate at a rate of 4 Hitpoints per minute instead of 1 Hitpoint per minute.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,14"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,14"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,15"
param=param_885,2
param=param_1274,struct_3066

// 1730
[struct_1730]
param=param_879,Double Cast
param=param_880,- The attack speed of all Magic spells and weapons is halved (rounded up).<br><br>- With +60 Magic Attack Accuracy (or +20 with Regular or Elite Void Knight Mage Armour) your binding and ice spells ignore accuracy checks against creatures.<br>Otherwise, your Magic attacks have 125% increased accuracy against creatures and 50% increased accuracy against other players.<br><br>- You save 90% of your Runes when casting spells. This includes charges when using powered staves such as the Trident of the Seas, Trident of the Swamp, Sanguinesti Staff and the Enchanted Slayer Staff.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,16"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,16"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,17"
param=param_885,2
param=param_1274,struct_3067

// 1731
[struct_1731]
param=param_879,Second Inventory
param=param_880,- Upon selecting this Relic you will receive an Extradimensional Bag which will act as a second Inventory with 28 slots.<br><br>- The Extradimensional Bag can be withdrawn from and deposited into from anywhere.<br><br>- The Extradimensional Bag can be opened so that items picked up from the ground will automatically go into it.<br><br>- Items can be withdrawn from a Bank directly into the Extradimensional Bag.<br><br>- Items cannot be used from within the Extradimensional Bag - they must still be in your Inventory.<br><br>- Existing storage items such as a Looting Bags, Herb Sacks and Rune Pouches cannot be stored inside the Extradimensional Bag.<br><br>- On death, the Extradimensional Bag is destroyed and can be reclaimed from the Sage in Lumbridge. The contents of the Extradimensional Bag are not destroyed when this happens.<br><br>- As this Relic gives you an item it must be unlocked at a Bank.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,18"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,18"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,19"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1274,struct_3068
param=param_1855,true

// 1732
[struct_1732]
param=param_879,Treasure Seeker
param=param_880,- Creatures that drop Clue Scrolls have a 1/15 chance of dropping them. This also applies to Impling Jars.<br><br>- Clue Geodes, Clue Nests and Clue Bottles are found 10x more often.<br><br>- All Clue Scrolls have the lowest number of steps possible for their tier.<br><br>- Every Clue Scroll casket will roll the max amount of rewards it can give. (It can roll the same item more than once) :<br><br>   - Beginner caskets will roll 3 times.<br>   - Easy caskets will roll 4 times.<br>   - Medium caskets will roll 5 times.<br>   - Hard caskets will roll 6 times.<br>   - Elite caskets will roll 6 times.<br>   - Master caskets will roll 7 times.<br><br>- There is a chance when opening a clue casket that you will receive another casket of the same tier. This is more common the lower the casket tier.<br><br>- There is also a chance for this additional casket to be upgraded to a tier above the one you opened.
param=param_884,"league_4_relics_large,9"
param=param_1853,"league_4_relics_medium,9"
param=param_1854,"league_4_relics_medium_off,9"
param=param_881,"league_4_relics,9"
param=param_883,"league_4_relics_off,9"
param=param_882,"league_4_relics_tli,9"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1274,struct_3069

// 1733
[struct_1733]
param=param_879,Unnatural Selection
param=param_880,- When getting a Slayer Task, you can choose which Task to receive. The same Task can be chosen repeatedly.<br><br>- Superior Slayer Creatures have a 1/25 chance of spawning.<br><br>- Superior Slayer Creatures always drop a Clue Scroll if there is one on their drop table.<br><br>- Superior Slayer Creatures now have double the number of rolls on the lesser creatures' droptable. This does not double the number of rolls on the Superior Slayer Creature's unique drop table.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,22"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,22"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,23"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1274,struct_3070

// 1734
[struct_1734]
param=param_879,The Botanist
param=param_880,- Farming cycles occur every 1 minute instead of every 5 minutes. (I.e. Your crops grow 5 times faster than normal.)<br><br>- Resources gathered from Farming are multiplied by 2x. Resources generated this way will not provide any additional experience.<br><br>- Mixing Potions always results in a 4-dose Potion, and there is a 95% chance to save your secondary ingredient.<br><br>- Stats boosted above their base level will no longer drain back down over time.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,24"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,24"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,25"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1274,struct_3071

// 1735
[struct_1735]
param=param_879,Infernal Gathering
param=param_880,- Upon selecting this Relic, you will receive a set of Trailblazer Tools which can be used with no requirements. The Pickaxe and Axe will do their respective skilling actions 0.6 seconds quicker than their normal tool equivalent, and the Harpoon increases Fishing speed by 1.2s. All three tools have the same bonuses as Crystal tier tools.<br><br>- Any ore mined with the Trailblazer Pickaxe will be smelted into a bar, and Smithing XP given, regardless of Smithing level.<br><br>- Any fish caught with the Trailblazer Harpoon will be cooked, and Cooking XP given, regardless of Cooking level. This will work even for fish that don't require a Harpoon to be caught if the Trailblazer Harpoon is equipped or in your Inventory.<br><br>- Any logs chopped with the Trailblazer Axe will be burned, and Firemaking XP given, regardless of Firemaking level.<br><br>- On death, these tools are lost and can be reclaimed from the Sage in Lumbridge.<br><br>- As this Relic gives you an item it must be unlocked at a Bank.
param=param_884,"league_4_relics_large,11"
param=param_1853,"league_4_relics_medium,11"
param=param_1854,"league_4_relics_medium_off,11"
param=param_881,"league_4_relics,11"
param=param_883,"league_4_relics_off,11"
param=param_882,"league_4_relics_tli,11"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1274,struct_3072
param=param_1855,true

// 1736
[struct_1736]
param=param_879,Equilibrium
param=param_880,You gain the following benefit to <col=#>All Skills</col>:<br><br>- Each time you gain XP, you gain additional XP equal to 10% of your total level.<br><br>- Additional XP given by this Relic is not multiplied by your Leagues XP multiplier.<br><br>- Your lowest skill will receive 20% total level XP instead of 10%.<br><br>Tip: Equilibrium will trigger per instance of individual xp provided, even if that is multiple times in a single tick. E.g. Production Master will trigger Equilibrium one time per item processed.
param=param_884,"league_5_relics_large,11"
param=param_1853,"league_5_relics_medium,11"
param=param_1854,"league_5_relics_medium_off,11"
param=param_881,"league_5_relics,11"
param=param_883,"league_5_relics_off,11"
param=param_882,"league_5_relics_tli,11"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1274,struct_3073

// 1737
[struct_1737]
param=param_879,Draining Strikes
param=param_880,- All of your attacks have 10% increased accuracy and 10% increased damage.<br><br>- Whenever one of your attacks successfully hits, there is a 50% chance that you will restore your Hitpoints and Prayer by 10% of the damage dealt. (Rounded up)<br><br>- This Relic does not work for multi-target attacks or Special Attacks.<br><br>- This Relic's restoration effect will work with the Scythe of Vitur's initial hit, however, it will only work for its secondary hits if those hits have the same target as the initial hit. 
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,30"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,30"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,31"
param=param_885,5
param=param_1274,struct_3074

// 1738
[struct_1738]
param=param_879,Exploding Attacks
param=param_880,- All of your attacks have 10% increased accuracy and 10% increased damage.<br><br>- Whenever one of your attacks successfully hits, up to 5 additional targets next to your opponent will also be hit. The damage dealt to these additional targets will be 100% of the initial damage.<br><br>- This Relic does not work for multi-target attacks or Special Attacks.<br><br>- This Relic will only work in a multi-way combat area.<br><br>- This Relic does not work with the Scythe of Vitur.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,32"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,32"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,33"
param=param_885,5
param=param_1274,struct_3075

// 1739
[struct_1739]
param=param_879,Weapon Specialist
param=param_880,- All of your attacks have 10% increased accuracy and 10% increased damage.<br><br>- Every 30 seconds, your Special Attack energy is restored by 30% rather than the usual 10%.<br><br>- Special Attacks that would normally have an energy cost of more than 20% now only cost 20% instead.
param=param_884,"trailblazer_relics_large,34"
param=param_881,"trailblazer_relics,34"
param=param_883,"trailblazer_relics,35"
param=param_885,6
