// 4335
[struct_4335]
param=param_1636,double_ammo_mould
param=param_1638,2000
param=param_1639,This double-sized mould looks like two ammo moulds, roughly put together with a metal strip.<br><br>It will allow for faster production of cannonballs, giving eight balls for two bars with each use.<br><br>Requires completion of the Dwarf Cannon quest to purchase.

// 4336
[struct_4336]
param=param_1636,kovacs_grog
param=param_1638,300
param=param_1639,Grog made by Kovac. This foul-looking brew will imbue anyone who drinks it with improved knowledge of Smithing.<br><br>Smithing: +4<br>Attack: -2<br>Range: -2<br>Magic: -2

// 4337
[struct_4337]
param=param_1636,smithing_catalyst
param=param_1638,15
param=param_1639,This fine powder helps smiths smelt bars. Bars made at standard furnaces using this powder will require half the amount of coal and reward twice the amount of XP. The powder will be consumed when used.

// 4338
[struct_4338]
param=param_1636,giants_foundry_ore_pack
param=param_1638,200
param=param_1639,A rather heavy looking package, packed to the brim with ores and minerals.<br><br>A pack contains 30 noted ores which could be any combination of the following:<br>   Coal<br>   Iron ore<br>   Mithril ore<br>   Adamantite ore<br>   Runite ore

// 4339
[struct_4339]
param=param_1636,smithing_uniform_torso
param=param_1638,4000
param=param_1639,A part of the Smiths Uniform. This piece of equipment provides a 20% chance to increase the speed of a Smithing action at an anvil.<br>This effect stacks when combined with other outfit pieces.<br><br>When the full set is worn, the chance increases to 100%.

// 4340
[struct_4340]
param=param_1636,smithing_uniform_legs
param=param_1638,4000
param=param_1639,A part of the Smiths Uniform. This piece of equipment provides a 20% chance to increase the speed of a Smithing action at an anvil.<br>This effect stacks when combined with other outfit pieces.<br><br>When the full set is worn, the chance increases to 100%.

// 4341
[struct_4341]
param=param_1636,smithing_uniform_boots
param=param_1638,3500
param=param_1639,A part of the Smiths Uniform. This piece of equipment provides a 20% chance to increase the speed of a Smithing action at an anvil.<br>This effect stacks when combined with other outfit pieces.<br><br>When the full set is worn, the chance increases to 100%.

// 4342
[struct_4342]
param=param_1636,smithing_uniform_gloves
param=param_1638,3500
param=param_1639,A part of the Smiths Uniform. This piece of equipment provides a 20% chance to increase the speed of a Smithing action at an anvil.<br>This effect stacks when combined with other outfit pieces.<br><br>When the full set is worn, the chance increases to 100%.<br><br>Can also be combined with ice gloves to gain the effects of both.

// 4343
[struct_4343]
param=param_1636,giants_foundry_colossal_blade
param=param_1638,5000
param=param_1639,A Giant Blade forged within the Giants' Foundry.<br>Normally reserved for the giants of Gielinor, Kovac is willing to part with this one, even though you made it.<br><br>Requires 60 Attack to wield.

// 4344
[struct_4344]
