// 4723
[struct_4723]
param=param_879,Superior Sorcerer
param=param_880,- Magic spells and weapons with an attack speed of 4 or above have this stat halved, rounded down.<br><br>- Magic spells and weapons with an attack speed of 3 or below have this stat halved, rounded up.<br><br>- You save 90% of your Runes when casting spells. This includes charges when using powered staves such as the Trident of the Seas, Trident of the Swamp, Sanguinesti Staff, Tumeken's Shadow, and the Enchanted Slayer Staff.<br><br>- Bind spells will always hit on an unfrozen, non freeze-immune target.<br><br>- Acquire the Arcane Grimoire, which allows you to change between any Spellbooks you have unlocked. Must be at a Bank to obtain the item.<br><br>- Acquire a Rune Pouch.<br><br>- All Rune Pouches store 2 more types of Runes.<br><br>- Magic attacks will deal an additional 25% as splash damage to surrounding targets, up to 5 additional targets.<br><br>- This splash damage effect only works in multicombat areas.<br><br>- Magic accuracy is increased by 175%.<br><br>- Magic damage is increased by 20%.
param=param_884,"league_4_relics_large,8"
param=param_1853,"league_4_relics_medium,8"
param=param_1854,"league_4_relics_medium_off,8"
param=param_881,"league_4_relics,8"
param=param_883,"league_4_relics_off,8"
param=param_882,"league_4_relics_tli,8"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1274,struct_4707
param=param_1855,true

// 4724
[struct_4724]
param=param_879,Brawler's Resolve
param=param_880,- Melee weapons with attack speed 4 or above have this stat halved, rounded down.<br><br>- Melee weapons with attack speed 3 or below have this stat halved, rounded up.<br><br>- 90% of charges are saved when using Melee weapons.<br><br>- Immune to all status effects, including but not limited to Poison, Venom, and Firebreath, with the exception of stuns and roots. This applies in both PvE and PvP.<br><br>- 10% Chance to deal a critical strike on a successful melee hit, dealing double damage.<br><br>- Melee accuracy is increased by 50%.<br><br>- Melee, Ranged and Magic defence is increased by 50%.
param=param_884,"league_4_relics_large,6"
param=param_1853,"league_4_relics_medium,6"
param=param_1854,"league_4_relics_medium_off,6"
