// 4727
[struct_4727]
param=param_879,Undying Retribution
param=param_880,- When you take fatal damage directly from an NPC or player, you will restore all your hitpoints and Prayer.<br><br>- Upon triggering this effect you will deal damage to all monsters or players within 3 tiles of you, assuming their south-west coordinate is within this radius. (Similar to how chinchompas and other AoE effects work). This effect will only work in the same scenarios that the Retribution Prayer would normally trigger.<br><br>- In PvM combat this damage will be equal to 200% of your Prayer level. In PvP combat this effect will be equal to 50% of your Prayer level.<br><br>- There is a 3 minute cooldown on this effect.<br><br>- Cooldown is reset on actual death.<br><br>- The damaging effect will not work on NPCs that are recoil immune, with some exceptions:<br>   - Nex<br>   - Hespori<br>   - Vorkath<br>   - All Wilderness bosses
param=param_884,"league_4_relics_large,18"
param=param_1853,"league_4_relics_medium,18"
