[struct_6440]
param=param_879,Woodsman
param=param_880,- All items are processed at once while <col=#>Fletching</col>. Stackable fletching items are capped at 10x the regular amount per action.<br><br>- Chopped logs are automatically burned while <col=#>Woodcutting</col> granting full <col=#>Firemaking</col> XP, this effect can be toggled above.<br><br>You also gain the following benefits to <col=#>Hunter</col>:<br><br>- 100% success rate on all actions.<br><br>- Traps attract animals faster, give double the loot and XP.<br><br>- Traps always drop a random herb seed or tree seed when harvested.<br><br>- Hunter rumours give double XP and <col=#>Hunters' loot sacks</col> will give an extra loot roll.<br><br>- All loot from jarred implings will give an extra loot roll and be noted. Additionally they will no longer break upon opening.<br><br>- All Quetzal Whistles will not lose charges.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,5"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,5"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,5"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,5"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,5"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,5"
param=param_885,1
param=param_1855,false
param=param_2574,league_relic_woodsman_toggle_list

// 6441
[struct_6441]
param=param_879,Barbarian Gathering
param=param_880,- You become capable of chopping wood, mining rocks and fishing with your bare hands without requiring any tools or bait.<br><br>- Your hands are equivalent to the crystal version of the respective tools where those exist.<br><br>- Whenever you gain <col=#>Fishing</col>, <col=#>Woodcutting</col> or <col=#>Mining</col> XP while gathering you will also receive an additional 10% XP in both <col=#>Strength</col> and <col=#>Agility</col>.<br><br>- Up to 3 different types of gathered items (wood, fish, metallic ore and coal) can be placed in the <col=#>Knapsack</col>, which has a total maximum capacity of 140.<br><br>- On failing to mine a rock, catch a fish or chop a tree you will have a separate 50% chance to succeed instead.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,1"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,1"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,1"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,1"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,1"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,1"
param=param_885,0
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,barbarian_knapsack
param=param_2574,league_relic_barbarian_gathering_toggle_list

// 6442
[struct_6442]
param=param_879,?
param=param_880,?
param=param_884,"league_5_relics_large,3"
param=param_1853,"league_5_relics_medium,3"
param=param_1854,"league_5_relics_medium_off,3"
param=param_881,"league_5_relics,3"
param=param_883,"league_5_relics_off,3"
param=param_882,"league_5_relics_tli,3"
param=param_885,0

// 6443
[struct_6443]
param=param_879,Hotfoot
param=param_880,While the <col=#>Searing boots</col> are worn, you gain the following benefits:<br><br>- <col=#>Agility</col> experience is gained based on your <col=#>Agility</col> level while you run.<br><br>- Caught fish are automatically cooked.<br><br>- Mined ore is automatically smelted.<br><br>Additionally, regardless of your footwear:<br><br>- Picking up some <col=#>Termites</col> or a <col=#>Mark of grace</col> from a course will automatically complete the lap granting completion XP and 10,000 <col=#>coins</col>.<br><br>- <col=#>Marks of grace</col> will always have a 33% chance to spawn on all rooftop courses.<br><br>- Completing a course grants two completion count and 25% bonus experience.<br><br>- 100% success rate on all actions for <col=#>Agility</col> and <col=#>Cooking</col>.<br><br>- You will receive 2x <col=#>Termites</col> from the Colossal Wyrm Agility Course.<br><br>- You will receive 10x <col=#>Crystal shards</col> from Prifddinas Agility Course.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,3"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,3"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,3"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,3"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,3"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,3"
param=param_885,1
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,league_relic_agility_boots

// 6444
[struct_6444]
param=param_879,Larcenist
param=param_880,You will gain the following benefits while <col=#>Thieving</col>:<br>- 100% success rate on all actions.<br>- You will automatically re-pickpocket an NPC.<br>- You will automatically re-steal from a stall.<br>- Items obtained from pickpocketing and stalls are noted.<br>- Stalls never deplete and guards will never catch you thieving them.<br>- The amount of coin pouches you can carry is increased by 10x.<br><br>Additionally, while <col=#>Thieving</col> loot is increased by 10x for the following:<br>- Pickpocketing.<br>- Stealing from stalls.<br>- Stealing house valuables in Varlamore.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,13"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,13"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,13"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,13"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,13"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,13"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1855,false

// 6445
[struct_6445]
param=param_879,Abundance
param=param_880,- All non-combat skills are permanently boosted by 10.<br><br>- Every time you receive an XP drop, gain an additional 2 XP in the same skill. This is affected by the League Passive XP modifier.<br><br>- For every XP gained, gain 2x as many coins. These can go either to your bank or inventory if there is room, which can be toggled above.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,2"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,2"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,2"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,2"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,2"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,2"
param=param_885,0
param=param_1855,false
param=param_2574,league_relic_abundance_toggle_list

// 6446
[struct_6446]
param=param_879,Transmute
param=param_880,The high alchemy and low alchemy spells transform into two new spells:<br><br>- <col=#>Alchemic Divergence</col>: Upgrades up to 10 of a resource into a higher tier.<br>- <col=#>Alchemic Convergence</col>: Downgrades up to 10 of a resource into a lower tier.<br><br>Both spells cost 1 <col=#>Nature rune</col> and have no level requirement. The spell gives 10 <col=#>Magic</col> XP for each item transmuted (before league XP multipliers).<br><br> The <col=#>Transmutation ledger</col> can be equipped and acts as an infinite source of <col=#>Nature runes</col>.<br><br>Using items on the <col=#>Transmutation ledger</col> will display what they can turn into.<br><br>When cast upon a noted item, these spells will automatically re-cast over time as long as the items are available in the same slot in your inventory.<br><br>You can still cast alchemy spells via the toggle above or by configuring the spells in your spellbook. Alchemy spells will not automatically re-cast.<br><br>List of Transmutable resources: <br><br>- Hides<br>- Runes<br>- Ashes<br>- Uncut gems<br>- Compost<br>- Seeds (Cactus)<br>- Seeds (Hardwood tree)<br>- Seeds (Fruit tree)<br>- Seeds (Tree)<br>- Seeds (Bush)<br>- Seeds (Hops)<br>- Seeds (Herbs)<br>- Seeds (Flower)<br>- Seeds (Allotment)<br>- Logs (Normal)<br>- Logs (Pyre)<br>- Mining (Normal)<br>- Mining (Crafting)<br>- Bones<br>- Raw Fish
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,11"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,11"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,11"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,11"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,11"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,11"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,league_transmute_book
param=param_2574,league_relic_transmutation_toggle_list

// 6447
[struct_6447]
param=param_879,Soul Harvest
param=param_880,While harvesting any farming crop, or when NPCs would drop bones or ashes, you will instead harvest stackable <col=#>Soul shards</col>.<br><br><col=#>Soul shards</col> can be used for the following:<br>- They can be used in place of <col=#>Pure essence</col> while training <col=#>Runecraft</col>.<br>- 100 can be sacrificed at the <col=#>Libation bowl</col> at the <col=#>Teomat</col> for 550 <col=#>Prayer</col> XP (before league multipliers) without requiring <col=#>Libation wine</col>.<br><br>You will receive 1 shard per 4 base <col=#>Farming</col> XP granted while harvesting or checking health while farming, this is not multiplied by the leagues XP multiplier.<br><br>You will receive more shards for higher tier bones and ashes roughly equal to the bone shard equivalent for that tier of item.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,9"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,9"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,9"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,9"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,9"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,9"
param=param_885,4
param=param_1855,false
param=param_2574,league_relic_soul_harvest_toggle_list

// 6448
[struct_6448]
param=param_879,Butler's Bell
param=param_880,When the bell is rung, a <col=#>Demon butler</col> will be summoned to work for you. The butler's work will continue even if you are offline.<br><br>The butler can gather the following resources for you:<br>- Mining ores (8 per minute)<br>- Catching fish (14 per minute)<br>- Chopping logs (10 per minute)<br>- Picking flax (50 per minute)<br>- Farming herbs (10 per minute)<br><br>Additionally, the butler can also process these gathered items for you but at half the rates listed above:<br>- Ores into bars<br>- Raw fish into cooked fish<br>- Logs into planks<br>- Flax into bowstrings<br>- Herbs into unfinished potions<br><br>When the <col=#>Demon butler</col> processes resources for you, he will share a 10 XP (before League XP multipliers) with you in the relevant production skill per resource.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,10"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,10"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,10"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,10"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,10"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,10"
param=param_885,3
param=param_2049,league_butlers_bell
param=param_1855,true

// 6449
[struct_6449]
param=param_879,Eternal Sustenance
param=param_880,Food is no longer consumed when eaten.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,15"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,15"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,15"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,15"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,15"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,15"
param=param_885,5

// 6450
[struct_6450]
param=param_879,Map of Alacrity
param=param_880,This item will allow you to teleport to <col=#>Agility shortcuts</col>.<br>- You will be sent to the less favourable side of the shortcut, or the starting side if it is one-way.<br>- Teleports can only be used if you meet all of the requirements to reach their location.<br>- Shortcuts retain all of their typical requirements.<br><br>This item ignores wilderness teleport restrictions.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,7"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,7"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,7"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,7"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,7"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,7"
param=param_885,2
param=param_1855,true
param=param_2049,league_agility_map

// 6451
[struct_6451]
param=param_879,Culling Spree
param=param_880,When you are assigned a <col=#>Slayer</col> task you will be able to choose from three different options. You will also be able to choose how many you wish to slay (5-200).<br><br>Where possible, at least one of the choices will be a boss slayer task.<br><br>Additionally you gain the following bonuses while on a <col=#>Slayer</col> task.<br>- Upon slaying a superior slayer monster, there is a 50% chance that another will spawn.<br>- Superior slayer creatures will always drop 1-3 <col=#>Clue scroll (elite)</col>.<br>- You will gain all of the the effects of a <col=#>Slayer helmet (i)</col> without needing to wear one.<br>- You can purchase any of the slayer reward store perks for free.<br>- The <col=#>Rune pouch</col>, <col=#>Herb sack</col> and <col=#>Looting bag</col> will be purchasable for free from the slayer reward store.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,14"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,14"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,14"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,14"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,14"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,14"
param=param_885,5

// 6452
[struct_6452]
param=param_879,Conniving Clues
param=param_880,When opening a <col=#>Reward casket</col>, you have a 1/3 chance to receive <col=#>Clue contracts</col> which can be consumed to teleport to your current clue step.<br><br>- Beginner clues give 0-2 contracts at a time<br>- Easy clues give 1-4 contracts at a time<br>- Medium clues give 1-5 contracts at a time<br>- Hard clues give 1-7 contracts at a time<br>- Elite clues give 1-9 contracts at a time<br>- Master clues give 1-10 contracts at a time<br><br><col=#>Reward caskets</col> also have a 1/4 chance to contain a clue scroll box of the same tier.<br><br>- Clues from creatures and impling jars now have a drop rate of 1/15.<br><br>- Clue vessels obtained from skilling (such as clue geodes and clue nests) are 10x more likely to drop.<br><br>- All clues have the lowest possible number of steps, and will give the maximum amount of reward rolls.<br><br>- Emote, Falo & Charlie Clue steps no longer have item requirements.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,17"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,17"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,17"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,17"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,17"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,17"
param=param_885,3
param=param_1855,false

// 6453
[struct_6453]
param=param_879,Flow State
param=param_880,The following actions all occur at a rate of 1.2 seconds (2 cycles) rather than their usual speed:<br><br>- <col=#>Mining</col> any rock.<br><br>- <col=#>Woodcutting</col> any tree.<br><br>- <col=#>Fishing</col> from any fishing spot.<br><br>- <col=#>Cooking</col> any food.<br><br>- <col=#>Firemaking</col> any logs or adding to a bonfire.<br><br>- Offering bones at a <col=#>Prayer</col> altar.<br><br>- <col=#>Fletching</col> the following items:<br>   - Regular & Atlatl arrows<br>   - Bruma Roots<br>   - Unstrung bows<br>   - Shields<br>   - Stocks<br>   - Javelins<br>   - Battlestaves<br>   - Hunter spears<br>   - Redwood hiking staffs<br><br>- <col=#>Smithing</col> the following items:<br>   - Smelting ores<br>   - Smithing bars<br>   - Making cannonballs<br><br>- <col=#>Crafting</col> the following items:<br>   - Glassblowing<br>   - Leather crafting<br>   - Pottery<br>   - Gold/Silver items<br>   - Spinning wheel<br><br>- The following <col=#>Farming</col> interactions:<br>   - Harvesting herbs<br>   - Harvesting allotments<br>   - Planting seeds<br><br>- Casting the following <col=#>Magic</col> spells:<br>   - Low & high alchemy<br>   - Superheat<br>   - Alchemic divergence & convergence (if unlocked)<br><br>- Additionally the following interactions in minigames will be sped up:<br>   - Wintertodt Roots and Brazier lighting<br>   - Tempoross fishing<br>   - Stealing Valuables<br><br>This effect stacks with the <col=#>Fletching knife</col> and <col=#>Diabolical worms</col>.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,19"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,19"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,19"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,19"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,19"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,19"
param=param_885,6

// 6454
[struct_6454]
param=param_879,Flask of Fervour
param=param_880,When the Flask is consumed:<br>- Your <col=#>Hitpoints</col> will be restored to full.<br>- Your <col=#>Prayer</col> points will be restored to full.<br>- Your special attack energy will be restored to full.<br><br>Over the next 2.4 seconds the sigil will:<br>- Trigger three explosions which deal 60% of your base <col=#>Prayer</col> level (30% in PvP) to all enemies within 3 tiles of you as typeless damage.<br>- Reduce all damage you take to 0.<br>- Not deal damage to <col=#>Yama</col>.<br><br>This item has a base cooldown of 3 minutes<br>- For every 10 damage you deal in a single hit reduce the cooldown 0.6s.<br><br>- This perk will also work inside The Gauntlet.
param=param_884,"league_6_relics_large,22"
param=param_1853,"league_6_relics_medium,22"
param=param_1854,"league_6_relics_medium_off,22"
param=param_881,"league_6_relics,22"
param=param_883,"league_6_relics_off,22"
param=param_882,"league_6_relics_tli,22"
param=param_885,7
param=param_2049,league_flask_of_fervour
param=param_1855,true

